{"tid":1533153,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★地產股累瀉19%　摩通憂有排跌","createTime":"2019-09-02T16:25:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T06:48:11.000Z","uid":19454,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4ee7a85b70a50744be8de67a9078e9db24c0af83","tid":1533153,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:25:03.000Z","msg":"摩根大通看淡香港地產股前景，直言即使股價已自高位回落19%，但仍未全面反映不明朗因素，包括中美貿易戰及香港政治事件或拖累經濟表現。該行更以「最熊」情景進行壓力測試，結果只有六隻地產股仍能維持確信增持的投資評級，四隻降至減持、兩隻降至中性，並全線調低地產股<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">目標價近7%至逾42%。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n摩通指，「最熊」情景下，樓價與收入比率由目前14倍下跌至長期平均數10倍，意味香港住宅樓價會下跌30%；若現時香港社會動盪不安，令到訪港旅客消費大減70%，本地消費亦減少10%，香港零售銷售貨值料下跌約三成，商舖租金可能要下跌30%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190903/bkn-20190903001405660-0903_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20190903%2Fbkn-20190903001405660-0903_00842_001.html&d=7ie9SmB3qTQYrTFhvLfIgQexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=c348a589\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190903/bkn-20190903001405660-0903_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"42e3c3b555138fce82ff7a1184133f2e20aca9bd","tid":1533153,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:25:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf2b92aa9483f900ca9f26fd083608975322125e","tid":1533153,"uid":103759,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:27:44.000Z","msg":"股票咋 唔包樓"},{"pid":"e88798a5322a7c4fe9f6b728a69f071678bd83d0","tid":1533153,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:28:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/LcZWxto.png\" data-th